data.title: All Day Baggage Storage
data.text:
Explore the beautiful city of Vancouver stress-free when you store your baggage with Gray Line Westcoast Sightseeingâ€™s All-Day Storage Baggage Service. Located at our Canada Place Cruise Terminal, you can access the baggage service daily between 8:00 am and 5:00 pm. Please refer to the FAQ section for additional details.

This service is a popular option for:

Disembarking cruise ship passengers who are not staying in Vancouver, but want to explore the city before their afternoon/evening flights leave.

Guests who arrive in the early morning and are unable to check into their accommodations until a certain time (Airbnb, guest homes, hotels, bed and breakfasts).

Guests with an overnight flight out of Vancouver who want to explore the city during the day.

We accept both large and small luggage pieces for storage, including:
